*fribidi-0.19.2-r2 (15 May 2012)

  15 May 2012; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org>
  +fribidi-0.19.2-r2.ebuild, +files/fribidi-0.19.2-glib-2.31.patch:
  Pass --with-glib=yes to ensure fribidi.pc has "Requires: glib-2.0" line wrt
  #345621. Only #include glib.h for dev-libs/glib >= 2.31 compability wrt
  #415721. Thanks to Thomas Sachau for reporting both bugs.

